{"tid":1060281,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（醫學JJ請進）出血性中風一問","createTime":"2019-03-13T16:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T01:44:21.000Z","uid":98387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b323f6cb74de79d10f00731f81f9764bd87de3ed","tid":1060281,"uid":98387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:26:00.000Z","msg":"事緣我哥哥，今年27歲，健健康康，平時無病無痛，仲一星期踢兩三次波。                                    上兩星期突然話頭痛，耳仔痛，一直在床上保持意識。係失去意識前醫務人員叫佢自行走出屋企門口上擔架床，隨後大叫頭痛耳痛後失去意識（想請問叫我哥哥自行走出門口會唔會令病情急速惡化？）                                                               之後送到天水圍醫院，再轉博愛醫院，最後先到屯門醫院，前後用左5個半鐘，到屯門醫院醫生話瞳孔已放大，無得做手術。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（想問下出血性中風就唔關時間長短事？因為醫生解釋假設直接到屯門醫院，一樣無得醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）                                                                            利申：借朋友ac問"},{"pid":"45a85df05bfc6b801ae6fb69fab085962c63adc0","tid":1060281,"uid":153496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a34330aa261539bad64c9001ff3fac41290dd80","tid":1060281,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁突然"},{"pid":"d9203b8cb2e023cfd218a051716dd661f0a12415","tid":1060281,"uid":103725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T17:01:59.000Z","msg":"缺血性先有得話黃金3小時/4.5小時嗰d <br />\n出血性無得做手術醫翻，要做嘅情況通常都係出血出到壓住個腦，顱內壓高等等，唔會話醫得翻好。"},{"p